ely 5 MJup smaller than any previous imaging survey that explored the\nsurroundings of Barnard's Star could restrict.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 5 Jul 2015 18:51:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-08-06"}
